### app/controllers/saml_controller.rb

🔹 Step 1: Login Action (Auth Request)

class SamlController < ApplicationController

    def login
        request = OneLogin::RubySaml::Authrequest.new
            redirect_to request.create(SAML_SETTINGS)
    end
end

NOTE::

    redirect_to request.create(SAML_SETTINGS)

This:

	Builds SAML XML request

	Encodes it

	Redirects user to ADFS login URL

	Sends SAMLRequest parameter

	User now sees ADFS login page. 